{"tid":702960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人其實可以過得更好","createTime":"2018-06-15T10:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T11:42:37.000Z","uid":181666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bd6f95bfaa1ac093dcd57f14147cac10e8ef4498","tid":702960,"uid":181666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:40:44.000Z","msg":"今日新聞<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭政府宣布，就明年底開始向入境旅客徵收稅項，用作支持旅遊設施基建和保育工作展開1個月諮詢期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180615/s00005/1529054928773\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180615%2Fs00005%2F1529054928773&d=YnwWlSBWHhr3D8QJ6eb0lL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=3901ac9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180615%2Fs00005%2F1529054928773&h=9dbf5900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180615/s00005/1529054928773</a><br />\n<br />\n之前去歐洲去廁所要比錢 最少都要<br />\nHKD5有時10蚊 15蚊。<br />\n搭車一程短既都要HKD17左右，就好似九龍灣去藍田甘短。<br />\n同埋d 簡陋 church上去都要成舊水。<br />\n<br />\n其實香港大可以交通工具 地鐵等收貴d 例如一程短既收15蚊 政府收取個差價 之後香港人就可以因為係香港人身份所以收返原價，港鐵個加價機制我唔L講住。 同埋廁所收5蚊。<br />\n<br />\n入境稅就言之過早，因為呢個有機會真係趕客，畢竟香港唔多特別野比人參觀。<br />\n<br />\n之後得返黎既錢就可以補貼香港人，或者起基建，因為香港仲食緊以前留落黎既基建老本，遲早要大修。"},{"pid":"0330e18d4ae858e11aa49e51591ef47731fbc1c4","tid":702960,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cabe422b4f2ddea92420cda3169000ccc31f332","tid":702960,"uid":181666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T11:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}